  <CalDefinition Description="Lag filter constant for use in filter algorithm for smooth transition between dimming values.  Value is an integer defined as a 16 bit unsigned fraction.  Default value is N-value, where E=(N/65535) is the filter constant. " Name="BRIGHTNESS_LAG_FILTER_CONST_GLOBALB" References="GIS-619-150 " Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
